OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784234868
OL,3,CArgentina risk Fifa action for
OL,4,Cdisplaying Falklands banner after semi-
OL,5,Cfinal win
OL,7,FIn 2014, Fifa fined the Argentine
OL,8,FFootball Association #20,000 after a
OL,9,Ffriendly against Slovenia because
OL,10,Fplayers held up a banner with the same
OL,11,Fsentiment.
OL,13,FArgentina boss Lionel Scaloni had said
OL,14,Fbefore the game he did not want the
OL,15,Ffixture to become about the conflict
OL,16,Fover the British overseas territory.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
