OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784234868
OL,3,CArgentina risk Fifa action for
OL,4,Cdisplaying Falklands banner after semi-
OL,5,Cfinal win
OL,7,FArgentina vice-president Victoria
OL,8,FVillarruel had described England as
OL,9,F"invaders" and "usurping pirates" in
OL,10,Fthe build-up to the fixture, and
OL,11,Ftweeted a victory message at full-time
OL,12,Fby saying, "it wasn't just another
OL,13,Fmatch" alongside a video of what
OL,14,Fappeared to be Argentinian soldiers.
OL,16,FShe also shared a photograph of the
OL,17,Fteam holding the banner.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
