OL,3,CArgentina risk Fifa action for
OL,4,Cdisplaying Falklands banner after semi-
OL,5,Cfinal win
OL,7,FPolitical tensions linger between
OL,8,FArgentina and Great Britain over the
OL,9,FFalkland Islands, which boiled over
OL,10,Finto conflict in 1982.
OL,12,FArgentina has repeatedly claimed
OL,13,Fsovereignty over the Falkland Islands,
OL,14,Fwhich are about 8,000 miles from
OL,15,FBritain and 300 miles from mainland
OL,16,FArgentina.
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
